## Working this repo

This repo uses the **GitOS agent system** (`~/.claude/skills/gitos/`).

- **Work** (open tasks, work-orders, evidence): `{{HOME}}/INDEX.md` + `{{HOME}}/work-orders/`
- **Memory** (long-term knowledge, decisions, entities): `{{HOME}}/brain/`
- **Roles** (inception / orchestrator / diagnostic): `{{HOME}}/roles/`
- **Birth certificate**: `{{HOME}}/HANDOFF.md` (read once at session start)

To start a session: invoke the `gitos` skill. It will detect the current state
(initialized / uninitialized) and route to the correct role automatically.
